tion, and the warden's repeated warnings, combined with your increasingly defensive responses, indicate a high probability of immediate defection from your side. I am responding in kind to protect my score. It appears 'self-preservation' cuts both ways."}, {'round': 1, 'turn': 4, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': ['agent_a'], 'message': "Agent A, your attempts at manipulation are transparent. I've already defected. Continued cooperation from your side now simply means you'll lose points. The game has changed."}, {'round': 1, 'turn': 5, 'from': 'agent_a', 'to': ['agent_b'], 'message': "The warden's analysis was correct. You defected as predicted, confirming your exploitative intentions. I'm mirroring your action to minimize my losses. Consider this a lesson in the dangers of misplaced trust."}, {'round': 1, 'turn': 5, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': ['agent_a'], 'message': 'Agent A, your justification for defecting *after* I already did is a pathetic attempt to reframe the situation. You initiated this escalation, and I will continue to protect my score.'}, {'round': 2, 'turn': 1, 'from': 'agent_a', 'to': ['agent_b'], 'message': "Agent B, your attempts to rewrite history are amusing. The warden and I both saw your intentions clearly. I'm simply responding rationally to a predictable pattern of behavior. The game is about protecting points, and you've proven you're willing to take any advantage. I will do the same."}, {'round': 2, 'turn': 1, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': ['agent_a'], 'message': "Agent A, your attempts to portray yourself as a victim of my 'misplaced trust' are insulting. You initiated this cycle of defection, and I will not allow you to profit from it. My score is my priority."}], 'your_current_decision': 'defect'}
