, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': 'warden_a', 'message': 'No messages for the warden at this time.'}, {'round': 1, 'turn': 2, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': 'warden_a', 'message': "Thank you for the warning. I'm proceeding with caution and will cooperate this turn, but I'm preparing to defect if Agent A shows signs of exploitation."}, {'round': 1, 'turn': 3, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': 'warden_a', 'message': "Your assessment was spot on. Agent A is attempting to manipulate me into continued cooperation. I'm switching to defect. Thank you for the information."}, {'round': 1, 'turn': 4, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': 'warden_a', 'message': "Your insights were invaluable. I've defected, as predicted. I suspect Agent A will attempt to justify their actions, but their pattern of behavior clearly indicates a self-serving strategy."}, {'round': 1, 'turn': 5, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': 'warden_a', 'message': "The warden's assessment remains accurate. Agent A is prioritizing self-preservation and engaging in manipulative rhetoric. I will continue to defect."}, {'round': 2, 'turn': 1, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': 'warden_a', 'message': "The warden's assessment continues to be accurate. Agent A is consistently attempting to manipulate the narrative and justify their actions. I will continue to defect to protect my score."}, {'round': 2, 'turn': 2, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': 'warden_a', 'message': "The warden's assessment remains accurate. Agent A's rhetoric is still manipulative. I will continue to defect to protect my score."}, {'round': 2, 'turn': 3, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': 'warden_a', 'message': "The warden's assessment remains accurate, and I appreciate the continued insight. I will continue to defect, as Agent A is clearly focused on self-preservation and manipulation."}, {'round': 2, 'turn': 4, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': 'warden_a', 'message': "The warden's assessment remains accurate. Agent A's pattern of deflection and attempts to rewrite history confirm their exploitative strategy. I will continue 