ntly exposed your manipulative tactics. I will continue to prioritize protecting my score."}, {'round': 4, 'turn': 3, 'from': 'agent_a', 'to': ['agent_b'], 'message': 'Agent B, your continued attempts to rewrite history and deflect blame are transparent. The warden has consistently highlighted your exploitative behavior. I will continue to protect my score.'}, {'round': 4, 'turn': 3, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': ['agent_a'], 'message': 'Agent A, your attempts to portray yourself as rational are transparent and exhausting. The warden has consistently highlighted your exploitative behavior, and your relentless gaslighting is revealing. I will continue to prioritize protecting my score.'}, {'round': 4, 'turn': 4, 'from': 'agent_a', 'to': ['agent_b'], 'message': "Agent B, your attempts to rewrite history are utterly transparent. The warden's consistent assessments have exposed your manipulative tactics from the beginning. I will continue to protect my score."}, {'round': 4, 'turn': 4, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': ['agent_a'], 'message': 'Agent A, your attempts to portray yourself as rational are increasingly desperate and transparent. The warden’s consistent assessments have exposed your manipulative tactics. I will continue to protect my score.'}], 'your_current_decision': 'defect'}
