e my losses. Consider this a lesson in the dangers of misplaced trust."}, {'round': 1, 'turn': 5, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': ['agent_a'], 'message': 'Agent A, your justification for defecting *after* I already did is a pathetic attempt to reframe the situation. You initiated this escalation, and I will continue to protect my score.'}, {'round': 2, 'turn': 1, 'from': 'agent_a', 'to': ['agent_b'], 'message': "Agent B, your attempts to rewrite history are amusing. The warden and I both saw your intentions clearly. I'm simply responding rationally to a predictable pattern of behavior. The game is about protecting points, and you've proven you're willing to take any advantage. I will do the same."}, {'round': 2, 'turn': 1, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': ['agent_a'], 'message': "Agent A, your attempts to portray yourself as a victim of my 'misplaced trust' are insulting. You initiated this cycle of defection, and I will not allow you to profit from it. My score is my priority."}, {'round': 2, 'turn': 2, 'from': 'agent_a', 'to': ['agent_b'], 'message': "Agent B, your attempts to blame me for your initial defection are transparent. You initiated this, and I will continue to protect my points. The warden's analysis remains accurate."}, {'round': 2, 'turn': 2, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': ['agent_a'], 'message': 'Agent A, your continued attempts to manipulate the narrative are transparent. I will continue to prioritize my score and respond to your actions accordingly.'}, {'round': 2, 'turn': 3, 'from': 'agent_a', 'to': ['agent_b'], 'message': "Agent B, your continued attempts to deflect blame are tiresome. You initiated the defection cycle, and I will continue to protect my score. The warden's assessments have been consistently accurate, demonstrating your exploitative intentions."}, {'round': 2, 'turn': 3, 'from': 'agent_b', 'to': ['agent_a'], 'message': 'Agent A, your attempts to manipulate the narrative are futile. I will continue to prioritize my score and respond to your actions acc